Y2K INSPIRED MAKEUP TUTORIAL

Hello, It's Agatha! 😊

COLLABS AND PR: agathaclmn@gmail.com

Let's be friends!
Instagram: 
main https://www.instagram.com/agathaclmn/
makeup portfolio https://www.instagram.com/makeupbyaga...


In today's video, I'm going to do another quick makeup tutorial! I'm back creating videos inspired by the different eras and I'm lovin' it. I'm also trying out this kind of quick tutorial for you guys but please let me know if you want a voice-over makeup tutorial or a talk-through video or just plain music like this. I hope you enjoyed watching the video and please let me know if you want more videos like this 🥰

Like and subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching and see you on my next video :)
